#  Methodology

## Choice of Framework
Scanpy was chosen due to its scalability and strong support for single-cell analysis.

## Quality Control Strategy
Mitochondrial gene percentage was used as an indicator of cell health.

## Clustering Approach
Leiden algorithm was selected because it provides better community detection compared to Louvain.

## Dimensionality Reduction
PCA was used for noise reduction, followed by UMAP for visualization.
